snippet.title: Resident Evil 3 - Launch Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/product/UP0102-CUSA14168_00-BH3B000000000001

Reach for the S.T.A.R.S.

Resident Evil 3 is out now on PS4, with Resident Evil Resistance included! Join Jill Valentine on her last escape from Raccoon City in Resident Evil 3, and join four other Survivors as they fight to escape from a Mastermind’s sinister experiments in Resident Evil Resistance.
